---
title: Easy Beef Pho Style Soup with udon noodles and fresh chilli pepper
description: This Pho style soup is bursting with Asian-inspired flavours and heaps of healthy veg. The main attraction of this dish, however, has to be the succulent cooked-to-perfection beef.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R12_W16_IE_IECLB14148-3_Main__7high-69f094e1.jpg
